column5: It might be a good thing that Jr is heading over,seems Gordon cant keep from spinning out.LOL  Wish I could of seen him STUCK in the grass.
You might have missed him stuck in the grass Brian, but of you check the standings, you'll still be able to see him stuck in first place.  Wonder how Deano made out??
Well we finally got to see the race, minus my sister and brother in law. I'll post more tomorrow.
